						               													<description>An adventure game based on the research of objects.&amp;#10;The first who will find all the elements that compose the 3 objects chosen at the beginning of the game will win.&amp;#10;Each object is made by 4 different parts, that you can find all over the islands where the &amp;quot;survivors&amp;quot; are settled.&amp;#10;When you think to have found your parts, you have to sign them with a pawn of your own colour, and when you think to have found all your pieces, you go to see the solutions cards: if you have the right pieces, you have won! ...On the other side, if you have wronged pieces, you have ended the game, letting other players try to win.&amp;#10;The background is a post-nuclear place, where the &amp;quot;survivors&amp;quot; must try to create all objects that they were able to use before the war (like the telephone, a bicycle) starting from singular pieces found on the islands, and to assembly them, to come back to the normal state of life.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
